      <item>
        <title>[Upcoming] New Twenty Twenty Frontity theme</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[mmczaplinski]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>We are busy at work on the 1.0 version of the 2020 theme!</p>
<p><strong>What will it feature?</strong></p>
<p><img src="https://community.frontity.org/images/emoji/apple/100.png?v=9" title=":100:" class="emoji" alt=":100:"> CSS to match the WP 2020 theme with pixel-perfection.<br>
<img src="https://community.frontity.org/images/emoji/apple/closed_book.png?v=9" title=":closed_book:" class="emoji" alt=":closed_book:"> Updated pagination to show links to intermediate pages like so: <code>1 2 3 ... 8 9 10</code>.<br>
<img src="https://community.frontity.org/images/emoji/apple/bullettrain_side.png?v=9" title=":bullettrain_side:" class="emoji" alt=":bullettrain_side:"> CSS transitions between pages!<br>
<img src="https://community.frontity.org/images/emoji/apple/scroll.png?v=9" title=":scroll:" class="emoji" alt=":scroll:"> Optional infinite scrolling!<br>
<img src="https://community.frontity.org/images/emoji/apple/bulb.png?v=9" title=":bulb:" class="emoji" alt=":bulb:"> Improved the lighthouse score!<br>
<img src="https://community.frontity.org/images/emoji/apple/ant.png?v=9" title=":ant:" class="emoji" alt=":ant:"> Many other small bugfixes and improvements!</p>
<p>You can see the work in progress in <a href="https://github.com/frontity/frontity/pulls?q=is%3Apr+is%3Aopen+label%3A%40twentytwenty">github pull requests</a>.</p>
          <p><a href="https://community.frontity.org/t/upcoming-new-twenty-twenty-frontity-theme/822/5">Read full topic</a></p>
        ]]></description>
        <link>https://community.frontity.org/t/upcoming-new-twenty-twenty-frontity-theme/822/5</link>
